1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:01,100
welcome back

2
00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:06,666
today we are going to use the stuff we crafted last episode to get into the electric age

3
00:00:07,133 --> 00:00:08,000
as per usual

4
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:10,033
we start with a steam turbine

5
00:00:10,033 --> 00:00:14,366
which shall go in a room dedicated to the first three tiers of electric machines

6
00:00:14,866 --> 00:00:16,700
we place our steam turbine

7
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:18,533
connect the steam pipe

8
00:00:18,533 --> 00:00:20,133
and prepare a line of cables

9
00:00:20,466 --> 00:00:22,866
we start our workshop with a wire mill

10
00:00:23,066 --> 00:00:24,433
then we shall have a mixer

11
00:00:24,433 --> 00:00:28,666
which will save us from having to deal with the crucible and the glass blow pipe

12
00:00:28,866 --> 00:00:32,300
an assembler to save us from using the create assembly line

13
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:34,700
a polarizer to save redstone

14
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,200
a centrifuge that while using a lot of power

15
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:41,166
will easily extract resin from kapok wood

16
00:00:41,566 --> 00:00:43,566
sparing us a lot of manual work

17
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,200
a chemical reactor with a fluid solidifier

18
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,133
to cheap out on rubber production

19
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:50,800
and before we decide what to do next

20
00:00:50,966 --> 00:00:54,466
we realize we barely have the power to run one of those machines

21
00:00:55,066 --> 00:00:58,166
so we channel all of our steam to our new bending machine

22
00:00:58,366 --> 00:01:00,600
which will allow us to make rubber foils

23
00:01:00,933 --> 00:01:03,266
with those we can indeed craft a pulley

24
00:01:03,333 --> 00:01:06,000
which will allow us to extract infinite lava

25
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,066
to power our new big bronze boiler

26
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:11,666
with this simple trick that engineers do not want you to know

27
00:01:11,866 --> 00:01:14,600
we have enough energy to run two blast furnaces

28
00:01:14,900 --> 00:01:16,200
there is just one catch

29
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:18,533
we do not have two blast furnaces

30
00:01:18,866 --> 00:01:21,200
not only we need more raw materials

31
00:01:21,466 --> 00:01:24,733
we should also complete a bunch of quests that are in the way

32
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:28,466
and the main issue is that we are asked to make some batteries

33
00:01:28,933 --> 00:01:32,200
usually the main annoyance is collecting the filling electrolyte

34
00:01:32,366 --> 00:01:34,700
here it is managing the poisonous lead

35
00:01:35,066 --> 00:01:37,166
to avoid getting our hands dirty

36
00:01:37,266 --> 00:01:39,100
we craft an LV miner

37
00:01:39,466 --> 00:01:42,266
which we shall power using water

38
00:01:42,266 --> 00:01:45,733
or more precisely, high pressure steam solar boilers

39
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,933
and once those heated up

40
00:01:47,966 --> 00:01:50,133
we started collecting some ores

41
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:52,566
we left the system run for a while

42
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:55,066
until we eventually managed to get lead

43
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:57,066
this is toxic stuff

44
00:01:57,166 --> 00:01:59,100
so we want to handle it with care

45
00:01:59,566 --> 00:02:01,333
we gently put it in our backpack

46
00:02:01,333 --> 00:02:04,100
and then throw it inside our processing machines

47
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:10,166
we keep moving the hazard like that from machine to machine until we finally get the battery alloy

48
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,533
once we manage to turn it into plates

49
00:02:12,533 --> 00:02:13,933
we have one more issue

50
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,266
we have to craft those into a battery

51
00:02:16,766 --> 00:02:21,200
luckily, we can upgrade our backpack to have a crafting table inside it

52
00:02:21,266 --> 00:02:25,133
which will allow us to craft the non toxic batteries inside the backpack

53
00:02:25,133 --> 00:02:28,100
without letting any dangerous dust come out of it

54
00:02:28,566 --> 00:02:30,466
but while that completed a task

55
00:02:30,733 --> 00:02:33,100
we still haven't completed the whole quest

56
00:02:33,566 --> 00:02:37,566
so we brace ourselves and take the poisonous material in our hands

57
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:40,700
that way, we completed the quest

58
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:43,166
and it looks like nothing else happened

59
00:02:43,733 --> 00:02:47,300
the thing is probably that lead is toxic only when inhaled

60
00:02:47,566 --> 00:02:50,666
unlike other stuff which will poison us on contact

61
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:54,133
but that doesn't mean we can fill our pockets with lead

62
00:02:54,733 --> 00:02:58,500
it appears that in huge amounts it's still toxic

63
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:03,166
for scientific purposes and to answer the question someone asked for a friend

64
00:03:03,333 --> 00:03:05,800
we figured out the maximum amount we can carry

65
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:09,700
is about many ingots and slightly more than half stack of raw mineral

66
00:03:10,066 --> 00:03:12,866
but if we crush it in a more dusty form

67
00:03:13,066 --> 00:03:15,966
we have issues starting from three crushed ores

68
00:03:16,133 --> 00:03:18,733
and if we grind it down into dust

69
00:03:18,966 --> 00:03:21,100
there's no way we won't inhale it

70
00:03:21,566 --> 00:03:24,133
anyways, after getting our lithium battery

71
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,966
we move on with our progression

72
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:27,800
we craft an LV ore scanner

73
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:32,100
which will allow us to use hacks to easily find endgame materials

74
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,733
which we can't even process

75
00:03:34,666 --> 00:03:37,400
once we find the stuff asked by the next quest

76
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:39,600
we lazily retrieve it

77
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,933
then, as suggested

78
00:03:41,266 --> 00:03:43,800
we work it to obtain some aluminum

79
00:03:44,133 --> 00:03:46,933
but while that was enough for completing the quest

80
00:03:47,133 --> 00:03:49,366
it's an amount that is basically useless

81
00:03:50,066 --> 00:03:51,366
considering our current situation

82
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:56,333
the best way to get more is to process some of the junk that our lead operation gathered

83
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,700
without crafting anything new

84
00:03:58,766 --> 00:04:02,166
we indeed managed to double our stocks of aluminum

85
00:04:02,366 --> 00:04:03,800
but to get even more

86
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:06,800
we can triple our yield with a thermal centrifuge

87
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:10,966
and while this gets (simplified?) by our new blast furnace

88
00:04:11,066 --> 00:04:15,766
we go back to our thermal centrifuge to work some sphalerite to get gallium

89
00:04:16,133 --> 00:04:20,700
this will be the easiest of the two components required for our next main objective

90
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:23,200
the second material required

91
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:26,700
is acquired by working our oldest nemesis, realgar

92
00:04:27,133 --> 00:04:28,800
with the help of our backpack

93
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:31,566
we process it until we extract arsenic

94
00:04:31,933 --> 00:04:35,600
and this was the other material we needed to mix up with gallium

95
00:04:36,166 --> 00:04:38,166
that will yield gallium arsenide

96
00:04:38,466 --> 00:04:39,800
to complete the quest

97
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,600
we have to take it in our hands

98
00:04:42,066 --> 00:04:42,900
as a reward

99
00:04:43,133 --> 00:04:44,766
our hunger bar is refilled

100
00:04:45,466 --> 00:04:47,000
once we retrieve our stuff

101
00:04:47,133 --> 00:04:49,100
we make smaller doses of that stuff

102
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:51,366
which we then input into an assembler

103
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:53,733
to improve the value of our efforts

104
00:04:53,966 --> 00:04:57,100
we process some oil sands into polyethylene

105
00:04:57,200 --> 00:05:00,300
which we finally add to the assembler to get diodes

106
00:05:00,733 --> 00:05:05,866
and I forgot that sometimes completing quests doesn't refill our hunger bar

107
00:05:06,133 --> 00:05:07,400
with those diodes

108
00:05:07,533 --> 00:05:09,700
we make our first MV circuits

109
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:15,466
meanwhile, our EBF completed the other thing required for unlocking the MV tier

110
00:05:15,766 --> 00:05:17,766
the first thing we do at this stage

111
00:05:17,766 --> 00:05:20,800
is build a clay line to get infinite goodies for free

112
00:05:21,266 --> 00:05:23,066
then we get the usual MV stuff

113
00:05:23,066 --> 00:05:26,733
and a pyrolysis oven which we use to get activated carbon

114
00:05:26,933 --> 00:05:31,266
that will allow us to get a gas mask filter to complete our hazmat suite

115
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:33,000
and with this equipment

116
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,633
we can now safely wash lead

117
00:05:34,633 --> 00:05:36,566
and use it to learn how to juke

118
00:05:36,866 --> 00:05:38,933
once we fully Learned how to carry lead

119
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,166
we use that to make some potin

120
00:05:41,333 --> 00:05:43,166
which is great for cheap pipes

121
00:05:43,666 --> 00:05:44,933
with those new pipes

122
00:05:44,933 --> 00:05:47,933
we can hook up a second boiler to a second EBF

123
00:05:48,133 --> 00:05:50,200
which we are going to run at HV power

124
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,933
so that we can melt kanthal

125
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:56,000
and this is going to be the material for the coils of our third EBF

126
00:05:56,266 --> 00:05:58,400
which will allow us to melt silicon

127
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,566
with that, we can make transistors

128
00:06:00,566 --> 00:06:03,333
and thus start our semiconductor industry

129
00:06:03,766 --> 00:06:06,500
however, as soon as we got some new circuitry

130
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:12,233
we realized we don't even have the infrastructure to run two blast furnaces at the same time

131
00:06:12,233 --> 00:06:15,733
so, before getting more energy hatches to fill the holes

132
00:06:15,933 --> 00:06:18,600
we work on a better power generation setup

133
00:06:18,866 --> 00:06:20,933
we now have a bigger main battery buffer

134
00:06:20,933 --> 00:06:22,500
powered by an alternator

135
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:24,433
powered by a big crete boiler

136
00:06:24,433 --> 00:06:27,200
fed by a robotic arm and a super fast pump

137
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:30,766
with that, we can now power our new HV machine array

138
00:06:30,766 --> 00:06:32,666
and fix our EBF issues

139
00:06:32,666 --> 00:06:36,700
with that, we are well set to grow our semiconductor industry

140
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,566
make more complex plastic

141
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,100
advanced chemistry

142
00:06:40,333 --> 00:06:42,100
research into nuclear fusion

143
00:06:42,266 --> 00:06:43,533
mess with living circuits

144
00:06:43,533 --> 00:06:45,866
and build a ridiculously large battery

145
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:50,766
but I think our new refrigerator which can stock food for a lifetime is all we need

146
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:53,133
we take off our heavy work clothes

147
00:06:53,666 --> 00:06:55,300
get a nice looking straw hat

148
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:58,566
and go relax with the nice breeze that blows on our crops

149
00:06:58,933 --> 00:07:00,900
and this is where we shall say goodbye

150
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:01,100
欢迎回来

151
00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:06,666
今天我们要用上一集做好的东西进入电气时代

152
00:00:07,133 --> 00:00:08,000
一如往常

153
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:10,033
我们先从蒸汽轮机开始

154
00:00:10,033 --> 00:00:14,366
它会放在一个专门容纳前三个等级电机的房间里

155
00:00:14,866 --> 00:00:16,700
我们把蒸汽轮机放好

156
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:18,533
接上蒸汽管道

157
00:00:18,533 --> 00:00:20,133
再铺好一排电缆

158
00:00:20,466 --> 00:00:22,866
我们的车间先从拉丝机开始

159
00:00:23,066 --> 00:00:24,433
然后再来一台搅拌机

160
00:00:24,433 --> 00:00:28,666
这样我们就不用再折腾坩埚和吹管了

161
00:00:28,866 --> 00:00:32,300
再来一台组装机，省得我们去用 Create 的装配线

162
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:34,700
再来一台极化器，省点红石

163
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,200
一台离心机，虽然耗电很多

164
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:41,166
却能轻松从木棉木中提取树脂

165
00:00:41,566 --> 00:00:43,566
省去我们大量手工活

166
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,200
一台带流体凝固器的化学反应器

167
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,133
用来省着点做橡胶

168
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:50,800
在决定下一步之前

169
00:00:50,966 --> 00:00:54,466
我们意识到自己几乎只够给其中一台机器供电

170
00:00:55,066 --> 00:00:58,166
所以我们把所有蒸汽都引向新的弯折机

171
00:00:58,366 --> 00:01:00,600
它能让我们做出橡胶箔

172
00:01:00,933 --> 00:01:03,266
有了这个，我们确实就能做出滑轮

173
00:01:03,333 --> 00:01:06,000
这会让我们提取无限岩浆

174
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,066
去给新的大型青铜锅炉供能

175
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:11,666
用上这个工程师们不想让你知道的简单技巧

176
00:01:11,866 --> 00:01:14,600
我们就有足够的能量同时运行两座高炉

177
00:01:14,900 --> 00:01:16,200
只不过有个问题

178
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:18,533
我们并没有两座高炉

179
00:01:18,866 --> 00:01:21,200
我们不只需要更多原材料

180
00:01:21,466 --> 00:01:24,733
还得完成一大堆挡路的任务

181
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:28,466
主要问题是，我们被要求做一些电池

182
00:01:28,933 --> 00:01:32,200
通常最麻烦的是收集灌注电解液

183
00:01:32,366 --> 00:01:34,700
这次麻烦在于要处理有毒的铅

184
00:01:35,066 --> 00:01:37,166
为了不把手弄脏

185
00:01:37,266 --> 00:01:39,100
我们做了一台 LV 采矿机

186
00:01:39,466 --> 00:01:42,266
准备用水给它供能

187
00:01:42,266 --> 00:01:45,733
更准确地说，是高压蒸汽太阳能锅炉

188
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,933
等它们升温之后

189
00:01:47,966 --> 00:01:50,133
我们就开始采矿

190
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:52,566
先让系统跑上一会儿

191
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:55,066
直到最后挖到铅

192
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:57,066
这玩意儿有毒

193
00:01:57,166 --> 00:01:59,100
所以得小心处理

194
00:01:59,566 --> 00:02:01,333
我们把它轻轻放进背包里

195
00:02:01,333 --> 00:02:04,100
再丢进加工机器里

196
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:10,166
我们就这样在各台机器之间来回转移这堆危险品，直到最终拿到电池合金

197
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,533
等它变成板材之后

198
00:02:12,533 --> 00:02:13,933
我们又遇到一个问题

199
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,266
还得把这些板做成电池

200
00:02:16,766 --> 00:02:21,200
好在我们可以把背包升级成内置工作台

201
00:02:21,266 --> 00:02:25,133
这样就能直接在背包里做出无毒电池

202
00:02:25,133 --> 00:02:28,100
还不会让任何危险粉尘跑出来

203
00:02:28,566 --> 00:02:30,466
但虽然这样算完成了一个任务目标

204
00:02:30,733 --> 00:02:33,100
整个任务还没做完

205
00:02:33,566 --> 00:02:37,566
所以我们鼓起勇气，把这种有毒材料直接拿在手里

206
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:40,700
这样就把任务完成了

207
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:43,166
看起来什么都没发生

208
00:02:43,733 --> 00:02:47,300
估计是铅只有被吸入才有毒

209
00:02:47,566 --> 00:02:50,666
不像别的东西，接触就会让我们中毒

210
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:54,133
但这不代表我们可以把口袋塞满铅

211
00:02:54,733 --> 00:02:58,500
看起来大量铅还是有毒的

212
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:03,166
为了科学，也为了回答某位“替朋友问问”的问题

213
00:03:03,333 --> 00:03:05,800
我们算出了自己最多能携带多少

214
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:09,700
大概是很多锭，再加上略多于半组的原矿

215
00:03:10,066 --> 00:03:12,866
但如果把它磨得更粉一点

216
00:03:13,066 --> 00:03:15,966
只要三块碎矿就会开始出问题

217
00:03:16,133 --> 00:03:18,733
要是再磨成粉

218
00:03:18,966 --> 00:03:21,100
那就不可能不把它吸进去了

219
00:03:21,566 --> 00:03:24,133
总之，拿到锂电池之后

220
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,966
我们继续推进

221
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:27,800
我们做了一台 LV 矿物扫描器

222
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:32,100
这能让我们靠作弊轻松找到终局材料

223
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,733
虽然我们连这些材料都处理不了

224
00:03:34,666 --> 00:03:37,400
一旦找到下一步任务要求的东西

225
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:39,600
我们就懒洋洋地把它收回来

226
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,933
然后照提示

227
00:03:41,266 --> 00:03:43,800
把它加工成一些铝

228
00:03:44,133 --> 00:03:46,933
虽然这足够完成任务

229
00:03:47,133 --> 00:03:49,366
但数量基本没什么用

230
00:03:50,066 --> 00:03:51,366
以我们现在的处境来看

231
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:56,333
想多搞点，最好的办法就是把我们在铅作业中堆出来的垃圾再处理一遍

232
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,700
不用再造任何新东西

233
00:03:58,766 --> 00:04:02,166
我们确实把铝库存翻了一倍

234
00:04:02,366 --> 00:04:03,800
但要更多的话

235
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:06,800
我们可以用热离心机把产量再翻三倍

236
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:10,966
虽然这一步已经被新高炉部分简化了

237
00:04:11,066 --> 00:04:15,766
我们还是回到热离心机，处理一些闪锌矿来提取镓

238
00:04:16,133 --> 00:04:20,700
这将是下一项主要目标所需的两个材料里最容易得到的那个

239
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:23,200
第二种材料

240
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:26,700
来自我们最老的宿敌，雄黄

241
00:04:27,133 --> 00:04:28,800
在背包的帮助下

242
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:31,566
我们一直加工它，直到提取出砷

243
00:04:31,933 --> 00:04:35,600
这就是我们还需要和镓混合的另一种材料

244
00:04:36,166 --> 00:04:38,166
混出来就能得到砷化镓

245
00:04:38,466 --> 00:04:39,800
要完成任务

246
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,600
我们得把它拿在手里

247
00:04:42,066 --> 00:04:42,900
作为奖励

248
00:04:43,133 --> 00:04:44,766
我们的饥饿条被回满了

249
00:04:45,466 --> 00:04:47,000
取回东西之后

250
00:04:47,133 --> 00:04:49,100
我们把这种材料分装成更小的剂量

251
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:51,366
然后送进组装机里

252
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:53,733
让我们的努力更值钱

253
00:04:53,966 --> 00:04:57,100
我们把一些油砂加工成聚乙烯

254
00:04:57,200 --> 00:05:00,300
最后再把它丢进组装机，做出二极管

255
00:05:00,733 --> 00:05:05,866
我忘了，有时候完成任务并不会回满我们的饥饿条

256
00:05:06,133 --> 00:05:07,400
有了这些二极管

257
00:05:07,533 --> 00:05:09,700
我们做出了第一批 MV 电路

258
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:15,466
与此同时，我们的 EBF 也完成了解锁 MV 等级所需的另一项工作

259
00:05:15,766 --> 00:05:17,766
这个阶段我们先做的第一件事

260
00:05:17,766 --> 00:05:20,800
就是搭一条黏土生产线，白嫖无限好东西

261
00:05:21,266 --> 00:05:23,066
然后再补齐常规的 MV 设施

262
00:05:23,066 --> 00:05:26,733
再加上一台热解炉，用来做活性炭

263
00:05:26,933 --> 00:05:31,266
这样就能做出防毒面具滤芯，补齐我们的防化套装

264
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:33,000
有了这套装备

265
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,633
我们现在可以安全地处理铅了

266
00:05:34,633 --> 00:05:36,566
还能用它来学会怎么走位

267
00:05:36,866 --> 00:05:38,933
一旦我们真正学会怎么带着铅行动

268
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,166
就可以用它来做一些白镴

269
00:05:41,333 --> 00:05:43,166
这东西特别适合做便宜管道

270
00:05:43,666 --> 00:05:44,933
有了这些新管道

271
00:05:44,933 --> 00:05:47,933
我们就能把第二座锅炉接到第二台 EBF 上

272
00:05:48,133 --> 00:05:50,200
我们会用 HV 电压去驱动它

273
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,933
好把坎塔尔熔掉

274
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:56,000
这将成为第三台 EBF 线圈的材料

275
00:05:56,266 --> 00:05:58,400
有了它，我们就能熔化硅

276
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,566
这样就能制造晶体管

277
00:06:00,566 --> 00:06:03,333
从而启动我们的半导体产业

278
00:06:03,766 --> 00:06:06,500
但刚拿到新电路不久

279
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:12,233
我们就意识到自己甚至没有足够的基础设施，同时运行两座高炉

280
00:06:12,233 --> 00:06:15,733
所以在补更多能量仓之前

281
00:06:15,933 --> 00:06:18,600
我们先把精力放在更好的供电方案上

282
00:06:18,866 --> 00:06:20,933
现在我们有了更大的主电池缓冲

283
00:06:20,933 --> 00:06:22,500
由交流发电机供电

284
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:24,433
而交流发电机又由一座大型混凝土锅炉驱动

285
00:06:24,433 --> 00:06:27,200
这锅炉则由机械臂和超高速泵供料

286
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:30,766
有了这套系统，我们现在可以给新的 HV 机器阵列供电

287
00:06:30,766 --> 00:06:32,666
也能解决 EBF 的供电问题

288
00:06:32,666 --> 00:06:36,700
这样一来，我们就能稳稳地发展半导体产业

289
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,566
做更复杂的塑料

290
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,100
推进高级化学

291
00:06:40,333 --> 00:06:42,100
研究核聚变

292
00:06:42,266 --> 00:06:43,533
折腾活体电路

293
00:06:43,533 --> 00:06:45,866
还造一块大得离谱的电池

294
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:50,766
但我觉得，能存上一辈子食物的新冰箱就已经够用了

295
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:53,133
我们脱下厚重的工作服

296
00:06:53,666 --> 00:06:55,300
戴上一顶好看的草帽

297
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:58,566
去享受吹过庄稼的微风

298
00:06:58,933 --> 00:07:00,900
这就是我们该说再见的时候

